{"tid":691384,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆連登狗狗拳擊大賽正式開始！","createTime":"2018-06-05T16:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T09:03:57.000Z","uid":40867,"like":8,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd5bf11d9f767eb628548b0bc1edef22972c0cc","tid":691384,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/001127_693ab192e0572afaf02bfa04229c8990.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F001127_693ab192e0572afaf02bfa04229c8990.png&h=bc2c8344&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/001128_693ab192e0572afaf02bfa04229c8990.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F001128_693ab192e0572afaf02bfa04229c8990.png&h=64a1e6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雙方係度試水溫！睇下對方實力如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/001304_67df8bc5777924aadc71ffaa33b415d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F001304_67df8bc5777924aadc71ffaa33b415d4.png&h=a7154a92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅狗忍唔住出擊了！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藍狗微笑應對！十分有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/001400_fa58c829132ee6c214dda72ab8159c78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F001400_fa58c829132ee6c214dda72ab8159c78.png&h=b41fcdf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍狗一手就黎個四兩撥千斤化解危機並令紅狗露出破綻！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/002902_9f6ed59c4f721eb9f257bf56656a206d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F002902_9f6ed59c4f721eb9f257bf56656a206d.png&h=b5a6b133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍狗馬上來一個大反擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f81915f9bed0155d8b17856c69f2496af6c4f77","tid":691384,"uid":134747,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  紅色係勝利嘅顏色"},{"pid":"d62d1bf87fd9e8b790a20879ae5f212f7fb07746","tid":691384,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b823d5590ff064cdaf956a3094ba5eea6b2372e","tid":691384,"uid":129521,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"兒登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b7a11902fd2fae105e69c33b87922c4938be38","tid":691384,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13fdebd00201ac478547bfa628798de3fed69af","tid":691384,"uid":99805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4b823d5590ff064cdaf956a3094ba5eea6b2372e","tid":691384,"uid":129521,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"兒登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T01:06:21.000Z","msg":"真係好似返緊小學咁"},{"pid":"e185947f4ab56721df439cb2eeb63c423b0d398b","tid":691384,"uid":35507,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"h